{"tid":709342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：不會對蘋果產品加關稅","createTime":"2018-06-20T02:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T08:01:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d52d0e671e41b0fe0bb2f9dd34d10116c36705ae","tid":709342,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"Login<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易磨擦不斷升溫，美國總統特朗普近日宣佈，將對中國進口總值 500 億美元的商品徵收 25% 懲罰性關稅。中國則揚言反擊，令市場憂慮貿易戰將會全面爆發。但有外媒引述消息指，特朗普已向蘋果 CEO 庫克（Tim Cook）承諾，他們不會受到加稅影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》引述消息人士指，庫克在上月拜訪白宮時，曾向特朗普表示向中國徵收關稅，將會對蘋果造成嚴重影響。而特朗普則向庫克承諾，政府不會對在中國製造的 iPhone 產品收取關稅。<br />\n<br />\n報道亦指出，蘋果近年不斷擴充在中國的事業勢力，年收入達500億美元，佔全球總收入近 25% 。但隨著中美貿易磨擦不斷升溫，讓長期依賴中國市場的蘋果成為夾心餅乾。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，美國政府早在 4 月提出的加稅名單中，已剔除了大量消費性電子產品。但在上星期公布的最新版本中，囊括了幾種不同類型的晶片，令科技業界擔人在貿易戰中受到牽連。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：紐約時報<br />\n<br />\n﻿ &bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=87cea723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=11c0b23e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a><br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=62538bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"2def6ec511c4c16333aa5e89cd57fd89695764f2","tid":709342,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b9cf63f4bdbac9845b98fdded7b20ba8d2a3f7","tid":709342,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"